  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New friends, welcome to Masa's tavern. In addition to drinking, you can also play our latest designed tabletop game - Mercenary Squad Auto Chess</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a light Roguelike Auto chess game that combines Diablo Brush Equipment Elements gameplay. Recruit mercenaries from various professions with different skills to battle the battlefield and fight monsters to the death. By flashing equipment, refining entries, and matching relics, build a super strong mercenary team and be invincible on the battlefield!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                                      </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/4aeebc0c3bdcef00b6a9e5e96c04419d.webp?t=1741958231\" width=200 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/ed6d92e0d0bbf4b39acd0b77e42a56ca.poster.avif?t=1741958231\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/ed6d92e0d0bbf4b39acd0b77e42a56ca.webm?t=1741958231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/ed6d92e0d0bbf4b39acd0b77e42a56ca.mp4?t=1741958231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>                                                   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/b907ea838e57d69d8fd54aa678a55253.webp?t=1741958231\" width=200 height=50 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/13aef90e5e30d7abb156b7d7dc6a83b6.poster.avif?t=1741958231\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/13aef90e5e30d7abb156b7d7dc6a83b6.webm?t=1741958231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/13aef90e5e30d7abb156b7d7dc6a83b6.mp4?t=1741958231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/f5c8d27892ca6605446a25d8a7fbca0d.webp?t=1741958231\" width=300 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/fbff8632579a8de08e3900bf4a6e99c7.poster.avif?t=1741958231\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/fbff8632579a8de08e3900bf4a6e99c7.webm?t=1741958231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/fbff8632579a8de08e3900bf4a6e99c7.mp4?t=1741958231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a simple and easy to understand game that doesn't require many beginner tutorials. With classic RPG elements, you can understand it right away. Recruit mercenaries, drag them onto the battlefield, and then start fighting. If there are enough coins, upgrade the store or recruit new mercenaries. If you can't defeat them, upgrade your equipment or replace it with higher quality or better equipment. No need to use too much brainpower, this is just a light Roguelike cultivation type auto chess game!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New friends, welcome to Masa's tavern. In addition to drinking, you can also play our latest designed tabletop game - Mercenary Squad Auto Chess</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a light Roguelike Auto chess game that combines Diablo Brush Equipment Elements gameplay. Recruit mercenaries from various professions with different skills to battle the battlefield and fight monsters to the death. By flashing equipment, refining entries, and matching relics, build a super strong mercenary team and be invincible on the battlefield!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                                      </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/4aeebc0c3bdcef00b6a9e5e96c04419d.webp?t=1741958231\" width=200 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/ed6d92e0d0bbf4b39acd0b77e42a56ca.poster.avif?t=1741958231\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/ed6d92e0d0bbf4b39acd0b77e42a56ca.webm?t=1741958231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/ed6d92e0d0bbf4b39acd0b77e42a56ca.mp4?t=1741958231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>                                                   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/b907ea838e57d69d8fd54aa678a55253.webp?t=1741958231\" width=200 height=50 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/13aef90e5e30d7abb156b7d7dc6a83b6.poster.avif?t=1741958231\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/13aef90e5e30d7abb156b7d7dc6a83b6.webm?t=1741958231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/13aef90e5e30d7abb156b7d7dc6a83b6.mp4?t=1741958231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/f5c8d27892ca6605446a25d8a7fbca0d.webp?t=1741958231\" width=300 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/fbff8632579a8de08e3900bf4a6e99c7.poster.avif?t=1741958231\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/fbff8632579a8de08e3900bf4a6e99c7.webm?t=1741958231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797080/extras/fbff8632579a8de08e3900bf4a6e99c7.mp4?t=1741958231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a simple and easy to understand game that doesn't require many beginner tutorials. With classic RPG elements, you can understand it right away. Recruit mercenaries, drag them onto the battlefield, and then start fighting. If there are enough coins, upgrade the store or recruit new mercenaries. If you can't defeat them, upgrade your equipment or replace it with higher quality or better equipment. No need to use too much brainpower, this is just a light Roguelike cultivation type auto chess game!</p>",
